# Portfolio Project (cl3menza.com)

## Trenutno stanje projekta (ažurirano)

- Stack: React + TypeScript + Vite + Framer Motion
- Entry point: src/main.tsx
- Stilovi: src/styles/global.css (kopija originalnog style.css)
- Komponente: src/components/layout/ (Header, Ticker, Footer, Layout)
- Sekcije: src/components/sections/Hero.tsx, TrustSignals, Systems, Flagship, Process, Stack, Contact
- Hooks: src/hooks/useReveal.ts
- App.tsx: mountuje Layout > Hero, TrustSignals, Systems, Flagship, Process, Stack, Contact
- Build: prolazi, npm run build → 0 grešaka
- LOCK fajlovi: index.html HEAD, src/main.js, src/style.css

## Conventions

- Preserve existing visual identity (palette, typography, motion feel)
- Use existing CSS classes from global.css

## LOCK fajlovi (ne diraju se bez posebnog odobrenja)

- `index.html` HEAD sekcija
- `src/main.js`
- `src/style.css`

## Do Not

- Replace premium feel with generic templates
- Add unnecessary abstractions
- Change design direction without approval
